title: Anyone seen 5G on T-Mobile in San Francisco?
content:
Pixel 4a (5G) on T-Mobile in San Francisco. I've had the phone for about 6 weeks, and I'm not ever seeing a 5G indicator. I have the requisite R15 Sim, the phone is set to favor 5G, and I've driven to the location where T-Mobile claims to have a 5G tower (Greenwich and Columbus). 

Anyone having any better luck?
